%F A008511 a(n) = (n+1)^4 - (n-1)^4 = 8*n + 8*n^3.
%F A008511 G.f.: 16*x*(1+x+x^2)/(1-4*x+6*x^2-4*x^3+x^4). - _Colin Barker_, Jan 02 2012
